## Limitations

The analysis is based on available data up to October 2023, and the rapidly changing nature of digital economies means that newer developments may not be captured. Additionally, the reliance on English-language sources may overlook insights from Chinese-language publications. The findings are also contingent on the accuracy and comprehensiveness of the cited reports and articles.